The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,

package for defining data structure to store simulation results. Please note the difference between object state and analysis result. 1) object state is for recreating the object 2) analysis result is for reporting purpose, such as security margin analysis.
